sentence: He's endorsing earlier and trying to oust at least 10 members of his party from the federal government, such as Wyoming Rep. Liz Cheney and Alaska Sen. Lisa Murkowski.
author: Virginia Aabram
title: Has Trump's seal lost its appeal?
